! Gecko Dry Adhesion Anchor

A reversible dry-adhesion contact model based on hierarchical micro/nano tip
contact rather than glue, suction, or hooks.

!! Why It Matters

This gives the flip-tile or hair-field material a real-world adhesion anchor
and a clear set of failure surfaces.

